  ],
  "remarks": "Dominique Kamanzi Ndarurutse is a Commander of the “Collectif des Mouvements pour le Changement-Forces de Défense du Peuple” (CMC-FDP), an armed group active in Eastern DRC and part of the so-called “Wazalendo” or “Volontaires pour la Défense de la Patrie” (VDP) coalition consisting of the Congolese armed forces (FARDC) and several other armed groups. This coalition fights against the coalition of the March 23 Movement / Congolese Revolutionary Army (M23/RDF) and the “Alliance Fleuve Congo” (AFC) in Eastern DRC and has been involved in human rights violations.",
